data.description: Move in Ready Colonial style home in Midlothian situated on a private 1.13 acre wooded lot in a cul-de-sac. This home is located in Reedy Mill subdivision and offers 4 large bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, complete with an attached garage with direct entry to the home through the mud room/ laundry area. Downstairs this home boasts a large living room featuring a fireplace with gas logs, a formal dining room, eat in kitchen with island and breakfast nook, laundry/ mud room, and a half bath. Upstairs, there are 4 large bedrooms and 2 full baths. The primary bedroom is complete with a walk in closet, en-suite bath, and water closet. Recent updates include: Downstairs flooring updated with LVP, Kitchen renovated with subway backsplash, butcher block counters, refinished cabinets, black SS appliances, and upstairs carpet replaced- all updates in 2022. Outdoors, this home offers gorgeous wooded views. Enjoy your morning coffee from the comfort of the full covered front porch or large rear deck. Roof replaced in 2018. Conveniently located close to shopping, restaurants, parks, and interstates/highways.
